{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.3\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">大卫逃避他儿子押沙龙时所作的诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">求助的晨祷</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.3.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>耶和华啊，我的敌人何其增多！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">许多人起来攻击我。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.3.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>许多人议论我：</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">“他得不到上帝的帮助。”（细拉）</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.3.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>但你－耶和华是我四围的盾牌，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">是我的荣耀，又是令我抬起头来的。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.3.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>我用我的声音求告耶和华，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">他就从他的圣山上应允我。（细拉）</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.3.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>我躺下，我睡觉，我醒来，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">耶和华都保佑我。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.3.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>虽有成万的百姓周围攻击我，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">我也不惧怕。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.3.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup>耶和华啊，求你兴起！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">我的上帝啊，求你救我！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\">因为你打断我所有仇敌的腮骨，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">敲碎了恶人的牙齿。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v8\"><sup id=\"Ps.3.8\" class=\"v8\">8</sup>救恩属于耶和华；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v8\">愿你赐福给你的百姓。（细拉）</span></p>\n</div>\n"}